Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月神基地司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆·西蒙斯叛變投敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當數量的敵人間諜滲透進入基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們決定將奪回月神基地的計劃付諸實施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止爭鬥 讓我們好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.28,0:00:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和解已經是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道伊澤爾坎特真正的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只為伊澤爾坎特大人而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須聽你的瘋言瘋語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊？ 月神基地來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來輪到我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根 出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久疏戰陣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一個水平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了嗎 吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有言在先 別想對我指手畫腳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的都是防守基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只關心能不能和高達交手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是你的個人復仇舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一的話沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…這算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 是我的菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想去討好傑哈特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我說中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在執行長官的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 該早點收拾了它才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒你的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 這邊交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識下 對聯邦絕望的人的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正與AGE-FX交戰的機體屬於聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師資料 顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被派往月神基地的王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德 本來是男性的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 她是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 用我的方式戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特他 並不是為了拯救維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須聽你的瘋言瘋語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特想 只留下優秀的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想親手 在聯邦和維甘中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行種群選拔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算為這種人賣命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說到這份上還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這點本事嗎 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是聯邦的機師對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又…怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話 應該清楚聯邦和維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩方戰鬥的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想結束這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你 和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是煩透了聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩透了那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子只有明哲保身的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼讓你變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根上校的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背景調查資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論過去如何 她現在投身維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的敵人這一點不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-1的強化改造馬上就將完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等離子潛航導彈的準備工作不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住 這場仗只有勝沒有敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著老機體口氣還不小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 吉拉德過去有過啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她 真正的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜·斯普裏根曾經是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛研製中機動戰士的試飛員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有一次 發生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我 你到底遇到了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和聯邦沒什麼話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你 怎麼可能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,評價試飛辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜·斯普裏根少校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴射器的點火機關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還要調整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭我會整理成報告的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天狀態還行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 比不上你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們作為同期機師相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相切磋進步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受著屬於二人的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 久等了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好久好久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時覺得 做試飛員也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得是因為當了試飛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蕾娜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺夢想也不再那麼遙不可及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有溫馨家庭的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為未來許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來增幅你們X-R能力的新系統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只需要收集實際數據
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行最終調整
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個已經通過了軍方安全基準
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情施展一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們前往進行測試飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 啟動新系統
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 提高功率
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗奈爾呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不聽使喚 請求中止測試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯普裏根呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統失控
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法控制動力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能下床
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟我回病房
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢 弗奈爾少校在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我 活了下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 我得知了事故真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管 提高輸出功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上頭的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統…失控
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們急於…獲得成果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是他的操縱失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他的死深表同情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是報告上說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的死是源於未按指示操縱系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從今日起特別連升兩級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命你為上校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我當個啞巴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出去亂說 最終對你也沒好處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候 我也保不住你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為保全新系統項目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以他的個人清白為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相被掩蓋了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與他約定的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被對聯邦的憎恨代替
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了復仇義無反顧拋棄聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應了維甘的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的戰鬥不會有任何結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我擁有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該用在這種事上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 說什麼天真爛漫的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份力量就是為戰鬥而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為完成復仇而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想用這份力量 阻止戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的機體跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你那裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒拜託你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑哈特大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人他不會拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一個部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在你心目中他是這麼好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說他是個值得尊敬的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬？就這麼簡單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想為傑哈特大人出力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助他開闢維甘光明的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少做美夢為好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼美夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生才不會像你想得這麼一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘必須被殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德小姐一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有要離開聯邦的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經不是聯邦的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯邦 已經不存在名叫蕾娜·斯普裏根的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我不是蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不能下床
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟我回病房
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢 弗奈爾少校在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·弗奈爾少校已經
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他始終和我同在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫吉拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 吉拉德·斯普裏根
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:24:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台高達馳騁天際時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場戰鬥被畫上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯哉 三倍高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thieleva是麥德納工坊提供給聯邦軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-R專用強力機體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.15,0:24:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和機師吉拉德·斯普裏根一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了維甘機體

